Install [Hubstore](https://github.com/pyrustic/hubstore): ```bash $ pip install hubstore ``` or upgrade Hubstore: ```bash $ pip install hubstore --upgrade --upgrade-strategy eager ``` Run Hubstore: ```bash $ hubstore ``` Then paste or type `pyrustic/demo` in Hubstore:
Enjoy !
